<h3 id="books">Books</h3>

<p>Reading has always been an essential part of my life. I read around 30 to 40 books a year, both fiction and non-fiction. If you are on Goodreads, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/42493361-alvaro-aguirre">add me</a> so we can keep each other posted on what we are reading.</p>

