<h3 id="home">Home</h3>

<p>I am originally from Ayacucho, a small city in the highlands of Per√∫. If you have heard of it, probably it‚Äôs because it was the place striken the worst by terrorism in the 80s and 90s. It is a very important place for me and my family, especially for the strong ties my grandfather had to the city (he even wrote a <a href="https://docplayer.es/59978426-De-huamanga-en-los-anos-sesenta-y-setenta-universitas-huamangensis.html">book</a> about it).</p>

<p>Ayacucho lies in the ‚ÄúCordillera de los Andes‚Äù, with mountains everywhere. This is a great map of the province:</p>

